data.description: You will love coming home to this 3 bedroom ranch located close to downtown Janesville with easy access to Hwy 51 for the commute to surrounding communities. Enjoy the spacious living room, nice size kitchen with all new stainless appliances and more!! The finished lower level provides you with more entertaining and living enjoyment. Still looking for more?? How about the great 3-season sun room overlooking your fenced-in rear yard?! Top all this off with a patio for grilling and an oversized 1 car garage!
